#: admin.php
msgid "Partytown Integration"
msgstr "Partytown Integration"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Unlike async/defer — which only delay loading but still execute scripts on "
"the main thread — Partytown runs third-party scripts entirely in a Web "
"Worker. The browser main thread is never touched: no layout jank, no TBT "
"penalty, no competition with user interactions. Officially tested compatible"
" services: Google Tag Manager, Facebook Pixel, HubSpot, Intercom, Klaviyo, "
"TikTok Pixel, and Mixpanel. Enable the Consent Gate to block scripts until "
"visitor consent is granted via the WP Consent API."
msgstr ""
"I modsætning til async/defer — som kun forsinker indlæsning, men stadig "
"kører scripts på main-tråden — afvikler Partytown tredjeparts-scripts i en "
"Web Worker. Browser main-tråden berøres aldrig: ingen layout-jank, ingen "
"TBT-straf, ingen konkurrence med brugerinteraktioner. Officielt testede og "
"kompatible tjenester: Google Tag Manager, Facebook Pixel, HubSpot, Intercom,"
" Klaviyo, TikTok Pixel og Mixpanel. Aktivér Samtykkeporten for at blokere "
"scripts indtil besøgende har givet samtykke via WP Consent API."

#: admin.php
msgid "Enable Partytown"
msgstr "Aktiver Partytown"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Activate Partytown service worker for third-party script offloading and "
"viewport prefetch. When disabled, scripts render directly on the main thread"
" with defer — useful for diagnosing Partytown issues (no Web Worker, no "
"consent gating)."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver Partytown service worker til offloading af tredjeparts-scripts og "
"viewport-prefetch. Deaktiveret = diagnostiktilstand: scripts afvikles "
"direkte på main-tråden med defer (ingen Web Worker, ingen samtykke-gating)."

#: admin.php
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr "Fordele"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Analytics scripts run in a Web Worker — unlike async, they never execute on "
"the browser main thread"
msgstr ""
"Analysescripts afvikles i en Web Worker — i modsætning til async kører de "
"aldrig på main-tråden"

#: admin.php
msgid "Viewport prefetch pre-loads product links automatically"
msgstr "Viewport-prefetch preloader produktlinks automatisk"

#: admin.php
msgid "Pagination next-page link prefetched 2 s ahead"
msgstr "Pagineringslink prefetches 2 s i forvejen"

#: admin.php
msgid "Bots and crawlers never receive Partytown (clean HTML)"
msgstr "Bots og crawlers modtager aldrig Partytown (rent HTML)"

#: admin.php
msgid "Automatic updates via GitHub Actions workflow"
msgstr "Automatiske opdateringer via GitHub Actions workflow"

#: admin.php
msgid "WP emoji scripts removed — saves a DNS lookup and ~76 KB"
msgstr "WP emoji-scripts fjernet — sparer et DNS-opslag og ~76 KB"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Third-party scripts auto-detected and offloaded to Partytown in one click"
msgstr ""
"Tredjeparts-scripts auto-detekteres og offloades til Partytown med ét klik"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Consent-aware: optional Consent Gate blocks scripts (text/plain) until "
"consent is granted via the WP Consent API"
msgstr ""
"Samtykke-bevidst: valgfri Samtykkeport blokerer scripts (text/plain) indtil "
"samtykke er givet via WP Consent API"

