msgstr "Partytown Version"

#: admin.php
msgid "Google Consent Mode v2"
msgstr "Google Consent Mode v2"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Global consent authority for all GCM v2-compatible services. Injects a full "
"7-parameter <code>gtag(\"consent\",\"default\",{...})</code> snippet in "
"&lt;head&gt; before any scripts load — with per-category consent signals "
"(marketing → ads, statistics → analytics, preferences → personalisation). "
"When active, scripts for GCM v2-aware services (Google Tag Manager, Hotjar, "
"LinkedIn Insight, TikTok Pixel, Microsoft Clarity) always run as "
"<code>text/partytown</code>. A revoke listener is automatically injected to "
"fire <code>gtag(\"consent\",\"update\",{...denied})</code> if the visitor "
"withdraws consent. <strong>Requires GTM or a gtag.js-based setup together "
"with a GCM v2-compatible CMP.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Global samtykkemyndighed for alle GCM v2-kompatible tjenester. Injicerer et "
"7-parameter <code>gtag(\"consent\",\"default\",{...})</code>-kodestykke i "
"&lt;head&gt; inden nogen scripts indlæses — med per-kategori samtykke "
"(marketing → annoncer, statistik → analyse, præferencer → personalisering). "
"Når aktivt, afvikles scripts for GCM v2-bevidste tjenester (Google Tag "
"Manager, Hotjar, LinkedIn Insight, TikTok Pixel, Microsoft Clarity) altid "
"som <code>text/partytown</code>. <strong>Kræver GTM eller gtag.js samt en "
"GCM v2-kompatibel CMP.</strong>"

#: admin.php
msgid "URL Passthrough"
msgstr "URL Passthrough"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Enables <code>gtag(\"set\",\"url_passthrough\",true)</code>. Preserves gclid"
" / wbraid parameters in URLs so conversion attribution works cookieless — "
"even when <code>ad_storage</code> is denied. Recommended for Google Ads "
"advertisers."
msgstr ""
"Aktiverer <code>gtag(\\\"set\\\",\\\"url_passthrough\\\",true)</code>. "
"Bevarar gclid / wbraid-parametre i URL-adresser, så konverteringsattribution"
" fungerer cookiefrit — selv når <code>ad_storage</code> er nægtet. Anbefales"
" til Google Ads-annoncører."

#: admin.php
msgid "Ads Data Redaction"
msgstr "Annonce-dataredigering"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Enables <code>gtag(\"set\",\"ads_data_redaction\",true)</code>. Redacts "
"click IDs (gclid, wbraid) from data sent to Google when "
"<code>ad_storage</code> is denied — enhanced privacy for visitors who have "
"not granted marketing consent."
msgstr ""
"Aktiverer <code>gtag(\\\"set\\\",\\\"ads_data_redaction\\\",true)</code>. "
"Redigerer klik-id'er (gclid, wbraid) fra data sendt til Google, når "
"<code>ad_storage</code> er nægtet — øget privatlivsbeskyttelse for besøgende"
" der ikke har givet markedsføringsamtykke."

#: admin.php
msgid "Meta Pixel Limited Data Use (LDU)"
msgstr "Meta Pixel Limited Data Use (LDU)"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Meta/Facebook Pixel does not support Google Consent Mode v2 — it uses its "
"own Limited Data Use (LDU) consent API. Injects an fbq stub + "
"<code>fbq(\"dataProcessingOptions\",[\"LDU\"],0,0)</code> in &lt;head&gt; "
"before Partytown and Facebook Pixel scripts load. The Meta Pixel always runs"
" as <code>text/partytown</code> — Meta applies LDU restrictions internally "
"(data not used for ad targeting). Your CMP does not need to block the script"
" via <code>text/plain</code>. Requires Meta Pixel to be added via the "
"Partytown Script List or an Inline Script Block."
msgstr ""
"Meta/Facebook Pixel understøtter ikke Google Consent Mode v2 — det bruger "
"sin egen Limited Data Use (LDU) samtykke-API. Injicerer et fbq-stub + "
"<code>fbq(\"dataProcessingOptions\",[\"LDU\"],0,0)</code> i &lt;head&gt; "
"inden Partytown og Facebook Pixel-scripts indlæses. Meta Pixel afvikles "
"altid som <code>text/partytown</code> — Meta anvender LDU-begrænsninger "
"internt (ingen data brugt til annoncemålretning). Din CMP behøver ikke "
"blokere scriptet via <code>text/plain</code>. Kræver at Meta Pixel er "
"tilføjet via Partytown Script Liste eller en Inline Script Blok."

#: admin.php
msgid "Partytown Debug Mode"
msgstr "Partytown Debug-tilstand"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Loads the unminified debug build of Partytown and enables all log flags. "
"Output is emitted via <code>console.debug()</code> — you must enable the "
"<strong>Verbose</strong> level in the DevTools Console filter (hidden by "
"default). Worker-side logs only appear in <strong>Atomics Bridge</strong> "
"mode, which requires the <em>COI Headers</em> option above to be enabled. "
"<strong>Use only in staging or local development — enables verbose logging "
"for all visitors.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Indlæser den uminificeret debug-version af Partytown og aktiverer alle log-"
"flag. Log-output sendes via <code>console.debug()</code> — husk at aktivere "
"<strong>Verbose</strong>-niveauet i DevTools-konsollen (standardfilter "
"skjuler det). Worker-logge fra web workeren vises kun i <strong>Atomics "
"Bridge</strong>-tilstand, som kræver at <em>COI-headers</em> er aktiveret "
"ovenfor. <strong>Brug kun i staging eller lokalt udviklingsmiljø — åbner "
"verbose-logging for alle besøgende.</strong>"

#: admin.php
msgid "Consent Architecture & GCM v2 Services"
msgstr "Samtykke-arkitektur & GCM v2-tjenester"

#: admin.php
msgid "GCM v2-Aware Services"
msgstr "GCM v2-bevidste tjenester"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"These services natively read the GCM v2 consent state and self-restrict data"
" collection — no text/plain blocking is needed when GCM v2 is active."
msgstr ""
"Disse tjenester læser selv GCM v2-samtykketilstanden og begrænser "
"dataindsamling internt — ingen text/plain-blokering er nødvendig, når GCM v2"
" er aktivt."

#: admin.php
msgid "Meta Pixel — Separate LDU Mechanism"
msgstr "Meta Pixel — separat LDU-mekanisme"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Meta Pixel does not implement GCM v2. Enable Meta Pixel LDU below — Meta "
"applies Limited Data Use restrictions internally."
msgstr ""
"Meta Pixel understøtter ikke GCM v2. Aktiver Meta Pixel LDU nedenfor — Meta "
"anvender LDU-begrænsninger internt."

#: admin.php
msgid "Consent Gate (WP Consent API)"
msgstr "Samtykkeport (WP Consent API)"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"When enabled, scripts are blocked as <code>type=\"text/plain\"</code> until "
"the visitor grants consent via WP Consent API. Requires a CMP plugin that "
"integrates with <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WP Consent"
" API</a>. When disabled (default), all scripts load unconditionally."
msgstr ""
"Når aktiveret, blokeres scripts som <code>type=\"text/plain\"</code> indtil "
"besøgende har givet samtykke via WP Consent API. Kræver et CMP-plugin der "
"integrerer med <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WP Consent "
"API</a>. Når deaktiveret (standard), indlæses alle scripts ubetinget."

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"⚠️ Consent Gate is enabled but the WP Consent API plugin is not installed. "
"Scripts will be blocked for all visitors."
msgstr ""
"⚠️ Samtykkeport er aktiveret, men WP Consent API-pluginnet er ikke "
"installeret. Scripts vil blive blokeret for alle besøgende."

#: admin.php
msgid "Script List default category"
msgstr "Script Liste standardkategori"

#: admin.php
msgid "WP Consent API category used to gate Script List entries."
msgstr ""
"WP Consent API-kategorien der bruges til at gatekeeper Script Liste-poster."

#: admin.php
msgid "Consent category"
msgstr "Samtykke-kategori"

#: admin.php
msgid "Checking for GCM v2 conflicts…"
msgstr "Søger efter GCM v2-konflikter…"

#: admin.php
msgid "⚠ Existing GCM v2 stub detected"
msgstr "⚠ Eksisterende GCM v2-stub fundet"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Another plugin or theme on your site already outputs a "
"gtag('consent','default',...) call. Running two GCM v2 stubs simultaneously "
"causes unpredictable consent behaviour — whichever fires last wins, non-"
"deterministically. Disable Google Consent Mode in the other plugin before "
"enabling it here."
msgstr ""
"Et andet plugin eller tema på dit site outputter allerede et "
"gtag('consent','default',...)-kald. To GCM v2-stubs kan ikke køre samtidig —"
" hvem der fyrer sidst vinder, og det er ikke-deterministisk. Deaktiver "
"Google Consent Mode i det andet plugin, inden du aktiverer det her."

#: admin.php
msgid "WP Consent API not installed"
msgstr "WP Consent API er ikke installeret"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Our GCM v2 update script reads consent state via the WP Consent API plugin. "
"Without it, consent signals cannot be delivered reliably to Google across "
"different CMP plugins."
msgstr ""
"Vores GCM v2-opdateringsscript læser samtykkestatus via WP Consent API-"
"pluginnet. Uden det kan samtykkesignaler ikke sendes pålideligt til Google "
"på tværs af CMP-plugins."

#: admin.php
msgid "Install WP Consent API ↗"
msgstr "Installer WP Consent API ↗"

