#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Enter your GTM Container ID or GA4 Measurement ID. The plugin injects the "
"snippet in <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> at the correct position — after the GCM"
" v2 consent default but before any other scripts."
msgstr ""
"Angiv dit GTM Container-ID eller GA4 Measurement ID. Pluginnet injicerer "
"kodestykket i <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> i korrekt rækkefølge — efter GCM "
"v2-samtykkestandarden men før alle andre scripts."

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Fetches the page HTML source and scans for active Google Tags (GTM, GA4, "
"UA). Only detects tags actually present in the rendered source — not plugin "
"settings. GCM v2 consent mode fires automatically before the detected tag."
msgstr ""
"Henter sidens HTML-kildekode og scanner for aktive Google Tags (GTM, GA4, "
"UA). Detekterer kun tags der faktisk er synlige i kildekoden — ikke plugin-"
"indstillinger. GCM v2-samtykkestandarden aktiveres automatisk inden det "
"detekterede tag."

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Follow the step-by-step guide to create your GTM container and let this "
"plugin inject and manage the snippet."
msgstr ""
"Følg trin-for-trin-guiden for at oprette din GTM-container og lad dette "
"plugin injicere og administrere kodestykket."

#: admin.php
msgid "Early Resource Hints"
msgstr "Tidlige Resource Hints"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Emits <code>&lt;link rel=\"preconnect\"&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;link "
"rel=\"dns-prefetch\"&gt;</code> for all configured third-party hosts in "
"&lt;head&gt;. Reduces TCP+TLS round-trip latency for first-visit page loads."
msgstr ""
"Emitterer <code>&lt;link rel=\"preconnect\"&gt;</code> og <code>&lt;link "
"rel=\"dns-prefetch\"&gt;</code> for alle konfigurerede tredjepartshosts i "
"&lt;head&gt;. Reducerer TCP+TLS-ventetid for førstegangssøgende besøgende."

#: admin.php
msgid "Partytown Health Monitor"
msgstr "Partytown Sundhedsmonitor"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Detects services that fail silently inside the Partytown worker (no network "
"traffic observed within 15 seconds) and surfaces an admin notice. Disable if"
" you experience false positives."
msgstr ""
"Registrerer tjenester der fejler stille inde i Partytown-workeren (ingen "
"netværkstrafik observeret indenfor 15 sekunder) og viser en admin-notis. "
"Deaktiver hvis du har mange falske positiver."

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"⚠ Partytown Health Monitor: These hosts produced no observable network "
"traffic. They may be failing inside the Partytown worker:"
msgstr ""
"⚠ Partytown-sundhedsmonitor: Disse hosts producerede ingen observerbar "
"netværkstrafik. De kan fejle i Partytown-workeren:"

#: admin.php
msgid "Performance Metrics"
msgstr "Ydelses-Metrikker"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"Collects anonymous TBT (Total Blocking Time) and INP (Interaction to Next "
"Paint) measurements from real visitors and shows rolling averages + P75 "
"percentiles in the admin — giving tangible proof of Partytown's main-thread "
"offloading benefit."
msgstr ""
"Indsamler anonyme TBT (Total Blocking Time) og INP (Interaction to Next "
"Paint) målinger fra besøgende og viser rullende gennemsnit + P75-percentiler"
" i admin. Beviser Partytowns fordele for main-tråden."

