#: admin.php
msgid "Partytown Exclusion Patterns"
msgstr "Partytown Ekskluderingsmønstre"

#: admin.php
msgid ""
"URL patterns (one per line) where Partytown is completely skipped. Supports "
"<code>*</code> wildcard. Useful for landing pages or payment flows with "
"scripts incompatible with the Partytown worker."
msgstr ""
"URL-mønstre (ét pr. linje) hvor Partytown springes over. Understøtter "
"<code>*</code>-wildcard. Nyttig til destinationssider eller betalingsflows "
"med inkompatible scripts."
